<p><img class="img_L_borderless" title="Summer Research" src="/images/SummerResearch.jpg" alt="Summer Research" width="200" height="133" />Undergraduate students in the Bourns College of Engineering are working with faculty mentors this summer researching everything from water quality to wildfires to materials that could lead to new medical devices.</p>
