<h3><br />Bourns Confers Degrees at Commencement</h3>
<p><img class="img_R_borderless" title="commencement 2010" src="/images/CommencementWeb.jpg" alt="commencement 2010" width="260" height="266" />The Bourns College of Engineering conferred more than 300 bachelor's, master's and Ph.D. degrees during its ceremony Monday, June 14,&nbsp;part of&nbsp;UCR's 56th annual commencement.</p>
